text: I won't be able to make use of the tablet this weekend so if someone would like it I can give it to you after class! Just let me know

Hey <!channel>, I just enabled *Calls* for our team, so you can ring a teammate directly from a Slack DM. Just click the phone icon on your desktop device to get started. You can find more information in this Help Center article - <http://get.slack.help/hc/en-us/articles/216771908>.
